

                                              WELCOME TO MY COMMENTS BLUERPINT 
                                              
                                         below you will see different class names or id's that are needed for the website to work with the front end html
                                
                                
                                
                                
                                
                                
                                
                                
 index.html   __________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
id="comment-input" (this is the comment text input meaning enter the text for the comment in this element)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
id="submitbtn" (this is the element that is clicked in order for the comment to be posted )
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
id="comments-section"(this is where the comments will be displayed meaning this is where the comments entered will show up)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
id="sortby"(this is a select element that is used to sort the comments )
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------


                
                
                
                
                
                
