signin.html
___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
id="signinForm"(this is the main container for the signin)
elementType:form or div
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

id="username" this is the element that should contain the users username in order to log in 
elementType:input or other text 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
id="password"this is the element thats value should contain the users password in order to log in 
elementType:input or other text 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________







___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
signup.html
___________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
id="signupForm"(container for the signup elements )
elementType:form or div
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
id="username" this is the element that should contain the users username in order to log in 
elementType:input or other text 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
id="password"this is the element thats value should contain the users password in order to log in 
elementType:input or other text 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
id="repassword"this is the element meant to confirm the password should be equal to the password element in terms of values
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
